<title>CANADA: TVX Gold Inc Q4 loss jumps after charges.</title>
<headline>TVX Gold Inc Q4 loss jumps after charges.</headline>
<dateline>TORONTO 1997-03-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			    1995</p>
<p> Shr	  loss	US$0.45		  US$0.00</p>
<p> Net	  loss	 72,770     loss	   425</p>
<p> Revs			39,834		   38,152</p>
<p>	   12 MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr	  loss	US$0.53   profit     US$0.06</p>
<p> Net	  loss	 85,955   profit	 9,414</p>
<p> Revs		     154,194		  156,948</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers)</p>
<p>Note: Loss follows charges of US$65.7 million in the fourth quarter and US$94.7 million in the full year, resulting mainly from the company's decision to suspend operations and dispose of bothe the Mineral Hill and Casa Berardi mines. Figures for 1995 were restated.</p>
<p>((Reuters Toronto Bureau (416) 941-8100))</p>
